         <div type="comments">
            <p><note type="parallels"><ref type="ms" target="txt:m-a268"/> (completing); <ref type="ms" target="txt:m-a305"/>; MaitrHami 16, 1-3, MaitrSiŋgim, Taf. 156</note><note type="philcomment">This fragment, which can be complemented by <ref type="ms" target="txt:m-a268"/> and supplemented with <ref type="ms" target="txt:m-a305"/>, contains part of the sixteenth act of the Maitreyasamitināṭaka. Uy. parallels are MaitrHami 16, 1b-2b17, and (according to <bibl><title corresp="ref:moerloose1979"/><citedRange>245-249</citedRange></bibl>) MaitrSiŋgim, Taf. 156 v.11-33 (<bibl><title corresp="ref:tekin1980"/><citedRange>130-2</citedRange></bibl>) for lines b6-7 (= <ref type="ms" target="txt:m-a305"/> a3-7). <ref type="ms" target="txt:m-a305"/> a1 and a2 = <ref type="ms" target="txt:m-a268"/> b4 and b5 respectively. The lacuna in line b6 in <ref type="ms" target="txt:m-a268"/> and here may be filled with <ref type="ms" target="txt:m-a305"/> a3. <ref type="ms" target="txt:m-a305"/> corresponds to MaitrHami 16, 2b2-3b24. See also <bibl><title corresp="ref:pinault1999"/><citedRange>202-203</citedRange></bibl>.</note><note type="remarks">Fragment of a manuscript which includes A 251 - A 294 (cf. <bibl><title corresp="ref:gengetal2004a"/><citedRange>64-65</citedRange></bibl>). Lines a8 and b1-2 are lost.</note></p>
