               <item n="m_philcomment_old">&lt;p&gt;This fragment, which can be complemented by [[A 268]] and supplemented with [[A 305]], contains part of the sixteenth act of the Maitreyasamitināṭaka. Uy. parallels are MaitrHami 16, 1b-2b17, and (according to [[Moerloose 1979]]: 245-249) MaitrSiŋgim, Taf. 156 v.11-33 ([[Tekin 1980]]: 130-2) for lines b6-7 (= [[A 305]] a3-7). [[A 305]] a1 and a2 = [[A 268]] b4 and b5 respectively. The lacuna in line b6 in [[A 268]] and here may be filled with [[A 305]] a3. [[A 305]] corresponds to MaitrHami 16, 2b2-3b24. See also [[Pinault 1999]]: 202-203.&lt;/p&gt;</item>
